{"tid":2398691,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"EXILE成員SHOKICHI嗒完明日花綺羅 帶美女返家過夜","createTime":"2021-02-07T13:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T14:11:51.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"b8d262550ea8429ec1a56f5be2a6a60abcddf355","tid":2398691,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/iVJjSvtpxqwxPG_V0gDqGGoflfs=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZJLKVO5SIVERLEJVYMD3KCFC3U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FiVJjSvtpxqwxPG_V0gDqGGoflfs%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZJLKVO5SIVERLEJVYMD3KCFC3U.jpg&h=3029cc3f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日本男子組合EXILE的35歲成員SHOKICHI曾經與前AV界天后明日花綺羅傳緋聞，兩人關係疑幻疑真，但他上月23日卻被日媒《週刊文春》影到去完桑拿後，到東京赤坂一間燒肉店，與一名長髮美女及男性友人聚餐，之後更與美女一同返回寓所，但該名女子並非緋聞女友明日花。<br />\n<br />\nSHOKICHI和明日花被指同樣都是出名愛「食肉」，換畫當食生菜。明日花的友人向雜誌爆料，指SHOKICHI在明日花前年生日時，送了一條巨型吞拿魚給她，還向友人介紹明日花為女友。明日花一向愛吃吞拿魚，收到重禮後亦在社交網站貼上吞拿魚派對的照片，兩人疑似玩認真。《週刊文春》又指SHOKICHI經常會邀請明日花回家搞男女關係，而明日花上載的自拍照更被fans發現背景與SHOKICHI的寓所相同。SHOKICHI後來因為避嫌，暫停邀請明日花回家作客。<br />\n<br />\nSHOKICHI上月偕美女A小姐坐車抵達寓所後，兩人前後腳落車，顯得非常謹慎。有知情人指，A小姐是在美容院工作，年約30多歲，而且喜愛夜蒲：「SHOKICHI與A小姐交往很久，A小姐很迷SHOKICHI，一有時間就會看他的社交網。」兩人在一夜春宵後，到翌日早上亦是前後腳出門，A小姐在SHOKICHI離開寓所後，40分鐘之後才獨自離開。SHOKICHI事後被狗仔隊追訪，但卻沒有任何回應，其事務所亦指不會理會他的私人事，至於明日花方面就回應指SHOKICHI是依照本能辦事的男人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/NJPXrKiNzL-ovR1PDaTM4tj0-dA=/802x637/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ST7PFFROKZE6VOJJGQEO2VOMVY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FNJPXrKiNzL-ovR1PDaTM4tj0-dA%3D%2F802x637%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FST7PFFROKZE6VOJJGQEO2VOMVY.JPG&h=b930c87a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/8BTQ5CeIG9aOV12z-27vv6r4K1Q=/802x622/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NAMSRALDWBA5BIZY5K5O4YNA2A.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F8BTQ5CeIG9aOV12z-27vv6r4K1Q%3D%2F802x622%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNAMSRALDWBA5BIZY5K5O4YNA2A.JPG&h=cee7c83c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ysuGzRSmff9sbIuX_1xqQ4fAvyM=/802x556/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IGQYJSZMLVCYBPOAOWBNN6X3QQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FysuGzRSmff9sbIuX_1xqQ4fAvyM%3D%2F802x556%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIGQYJSZMLVCYBPOAOWBNN6X3QQ.JPG&h=54c08c06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/hhKbQB8YfcW8JV5bQshtlRqSHxU=/802x934/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ZK6UPQVGWZD6VKMAQB2OXY3X5I.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FhhKbQB8YfcW8JV5bQshtlRqSHxU%3D%2F802x934%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FZK6UPQVGWZD6VKMAQB2OXY3X5I.JPG&h=f9de7a86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2Q5_8ltgSS4xA66ny5408X_8Mp0=/802x1006/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/H654ZREKJZAVZKLT5BSONWY4DI.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2Q5_8ltgSS4xA66ny5408X_8Mp0%3D%2F802x1006%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FH654ZREKJZAVZKLT5BSONWY4DI.JPG&h=c4b77275&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"912f1040640a81306139e6e7e3c64059a727fc3f","tid":2398691,"uid":378357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:47:49.000Z","msg":"WFC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6b3bddbc953faf1faf2bc0b5aa88e63d867bb69","tid":2398691,"uid":118346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:47:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90365230aa51a14c4554e84bbc3d4ebf52d241fd","tid":2398691,"uid":391165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T13:48:41.000Z","msg":"兩個都見過全裸"},{"pid":"1ba2d9a38f63ae7e6124723f9443bbb1d99d183c","tid":2398691,"uid":261849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T14:11:51.000Z","msg":"無興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}